From 262da2bdb74d11b9e38863ef55949371cd18c5d5 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>
Date: Sat, 16 May 2026 12:50:34 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 3/8] Redesign job + work order detail, settings, trial banner

- Job detail: breadcrumb header with pill row, quick-assign card,
  ready-to-invoice orange-soft callout, .grid-2 layout with checklist /
  photos / change orders / billing table / costing on the left and
  status actions / property / assigned workers / time / WO origin in
  the right rail.
- Work order detail: pill row + breadcrumb, two-column layout with
  description, photos, PM comments threaded under cards, decision and
  PM contact cards.
- Settings layout: v1 page-h with kicker, sidebar nav as a
  .card with active-state highlight.
- TrialBanner: paper banner with orange-soft / red-soft tones and
  v1 buttons (dark ink CTA), replacing the old solid amber bar.
